      <title>Prospect Medical 签署临时协议以避免医院关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/prospect-medical-signs-temporary-deal-to-avert-hospital-closures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[破产的医疗系统 Prospect Medical Holdings Inc. 获得法院批准，将其宾夕法尼亚州医院的运营移交给一家政府支持的接管人，这是一项最后一刻达成的协议，避免了重要医疗中心可能关闭的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/prospect-medical-signs-temporary-deal-to-avert-hospital-closures</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 23:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
